summary: Look I don’t want to start shit, but let’s be clear. The problem with tuffy4life wasn’t that the fandom was too stupid to grasp...
body: Look I don’t want to start shit, but let’s be clear. The problem with tuffy4life wasn’t that the fandom was too stupid to grasp the joke. Pretty much everyone did. However, any joke gets old after the fiftieth time, and doing nothing but flooding the tag with something so unnecessarily bitter is extremely irritating. If you guys just apologized instead of trying to make the fandom out to be a bunch of crybabies who can’t understand satire there wouldn’t be a problem. Would it have really been that hard to just acknowledge it went too far without swiping at the fandom?
